portsIn.value: This is where                 comes into play.

portsIn.name: String 7

portsIn.name: value
portsIn.value: Right now some companies are using your data to send you ads for things you might be interested in, but the systems behind this are capable of much more. Everything from targeting mentally unstable people in desperate times to emulating your behaviour is possible. Sadly the mindset of nothing to hide - nothing to fear only works, if the people in control share all your personal beliefs & values and will continue to do so.

portsIn.name: value
portsIn.value: Well, I did. My name is Paul, I am 24 years old and this is basically my thesis project. I have absolutely no background in computer science. I am basically just some design student who wanted to make something useful, which in my testing at least, this program has become. I am particularly fond of the idea of spreading data for data security purposes, but my coding skills are definitely not my strong suit.
